<div class="table-wrapper"><table><thead><tr><th>Olay AdÄ±</th><th>Callback ArgÃ¼manlarÄ±</th><th>Ne Zaman YayÄ±nlanÄ±r</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>'error'</code></td><td><code>(error)</code></td><td>Sunucu seviyesinde bir hata oluÅŸtuÄŸunda</td></tr></tbody></table></div>

